article.description: — Jaylen Sims had 24 points as UNC Wilmington defeated UNC Asheville 76-68 on Friday.
article.headline: Sims carries UNC-Wilmington over UNC-Asheville 76-68
article.story: ASHEVILLE, N.C. -- — Jaylen Sims had 24 points as UNC Wilmington defeated UNC Asheville 76-68 on Friday. Jake Boggs had 19 points and three blocks for UNC Wilmington (1-1). Mike Okauru added 14 points and 10 rebounds and Ty Gadsden had 12 points. Trent Stephney had 14 points for the Bulldogs (0-1). Tajion Jones and Evan Clayborne each had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
